11: Wh-what do you think, Captain Alk?
20:
Th-thank you! Now, we've gotta call
everyone in for a taste-test—
32:
P-Parfait?! Th-this isn't anything a
pro like you would like—
36: ...Never mind. Please, give it a try!
54:
It really is! Hard to believe it was
made by a beginner!
63:
Hm? Your words seem to lack
conviction.
67:
S-sorry... I am thankful for your
kindness.
69:
However... A store-bought cake
would've been much better.
73:
You're overthinking it. Beginners
shouldn't compare themselves to
pros.
77:
S-sure, but I'm sure everybody
would've been happier eating
something tastier, made by
someone else...
82:
...What kind of cake do you want to
make for everyone during the
holidays, Fluffy?
89:
I don't know. I don't know anything
about this holiday season, about the
children I'd give the cake to...
97:
In that case, why don't we start with
getting you acquainted with the
season!
108:
Thanks for all your hard work getting
things set up today, everyone! The
Guild has prepared a little treat for
you all!
110:
I hope it'll keep you going during the
hustle and bustle of the season!
118:
Wow! So this is what the holidays
are like?
122:
It's just a party, and a pretty peculiar
one at that.
124:
But it gives off a festive atmosphere
all the same!
129: It sure does! I can't help but smile!
137:
N-no...
I was just thinking... Parfait's in
charge of the kitchen today, isn't she?
142:
Heh. Well, it doesn't taste like her
trademark Monster Cuisine this time.
156:
Sorry for the wait, everyone! The
holiday cake's all finished!
166:
Heh-heh! I can see I've got
everyone's attention... But this cake
isn't what you think it is!
177:
Looks like Monster Cuisine's on the
menu, after all!
182:
Don't worry, I promise it tastes great!
And it looks a lot more appetizing
than my previous efforts!
187:
Surely that doesn't matter if your
creation can walk!
192:
Now then, Fluffy! Would you do the
honors and cut the cake for us?
212:
I was wondering how things would
turn out with the cake, but somehow
or other I think we all had fun.
225:
...But, uh, Fluffy? Nobody's forcing
you to have fun, either.
227:
Today's party was just my own way
of celebrating the holidays.
230:
What about you, Fluffy? How do you
want to celebrate?
238:
First of all, don't compare yourself to
others and what they're doing.
240:
If there's something you want to
share with others, then you're the
only one who can do that properly.
245:
...I want to make a cake that brings
a big smile to everyone's face.
254:
...But, I'm not good enough to make
something like that yet.
258:
That's why I need your help! Please,
teach me all about baking a cake!
276:
I'll make a cake that brings joy to all
of you!
